Installation Steps
1. run update.sh
2. Append 'Play' to module names
3. change build directory to $SRCROOT/lib/play
4. Erase Loader from Framework_Vulkan, replace with Loader inn PVPlayCore/Core
5. Run python3 	xcode_absolute_path_to_relative.py  
6. Erase CMakefiles / .cmake / .make files
7. Add Loader.cpp / and other files in PVPlayCore/Play to appropriate project (PlayCore)
